MODULE DEPENDENCIES - dependencies from Maven or Ivy repository

FILE DEPENDENCIES

SCOPES:
  api (it packs all dependencies to your app file jar or war)
  implementation (dependencies are only during development and build. No dependencies in jar or war)
  testImplementation (only during test phase)
  compileOnly (is still valid. It was added in 3.0 to replace provided and not compile)
  
OLD VERSION SCOPES:
  compile (replaced by api and implementation)
  testCompile (replaced with testImplementation)
  debugCompile (replaced with debugImplementation, can't find info about it in the Internet...)
  androidTestCompile (replaced with androidTestImplementation,  can't find info about it in the Internet)
  
